    "ideation": "The division sign represents separation, fragmentation, and cold mathematical logic. In this animation, the face performs as the symbol itself. The 'dots' of the division sign are personified by the eyes, which start as a single unit and are then forced apart by a growing horizontal 'bar' (the mouth). The emotional arc is one of clinical disassembly: the eyes move from a shared focus to an extreme vertical split, while the mouth transitions from a thin, surgical line to a thick, vibrating horizontal divider. The color palette utilizes calculating blues and slate grays, emphasizing a sterile, algorithmic process of breaking something into its constituent parts.",
